                <h1>E-Verify Background Checks: What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>An e-verify background check is a vital tool for employers to confirm an employee's eligibility to work in the United States. This electronic system checks the information provided in the employee's I-9 form against government records. Utilizing e-verify helps prevent unauthorized employment and ensures compliance with immigration laws.</p>
